ess, Budapest, pp.&nbsp;228\u201353. {{ISBN|978-963-9776-76-0}}.\n\n== External links ==\n{{Z148}}\n{{Commons category|Romani people}}\n\n'''European countries Roma links'''\n* {{Citation |url = http://www.sintiundroma.de/en/sinti-roma.html |title = History the Roma and Sinti in Germany }}.\n* {{Citation |place = [[Austria|AT]] |chapter-url = http://romafacts.uni-graz.at/index.php/history/general-introduction/general-introduction |title = History of the Roma in Austria |chapter = General introduction |publisher = Uni Graz }}.\n* {{cite web |url = http://www.rommuz.cz/en/history-and-language/ |archive-url = https://archive.is/20131028133534/http://www.rommuz.cz/en/history-and-language/ |url-status=dead |archive-date = 28 October 2013 |title = History of the Roma in Czech Republic |publisher = Rommuz |place = CZ }}.\n* {{Citation |url = http://www.romasinti.eu/#/ZoniWeisz/Deportation |title = Deportation |publisher = Romas Inti |place = [[European Union|EU]] }}.  History of some Roma Europeans\n* {{Citation |title = Gypsies in France, 1566\u20132011 |url = http://www.fyifrance.com/gypsybib.htm |publisher = FYI France }}\n; The concentration, labor, ghetto camps that the Roma were persecuted in during World War II\n* {{Citation |url = http://en.auschwitz.org/h/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=11&Itemid=3 |title = Auschwitz }}.\n* {{Citation |contribution-url = http://www.holocaust.cz/en/history/camps/hodonin |title = History: Camps |contribution = Hodonin |publisher = Holocaus |place = CZ }}.\n* {{Citation |url = http://www.lety-memorial.cz/history_en.aspx |title = History |publisher = Lety memorial |place = CZ }}.\n* {{cite web |url = http://www.europarl.eu.int/omk/sipade3?SAME_LEVEL=1&LEVEL=5&NAV=X&DETAIL=&PUBREF=-//EP//TEXT+TA+P6-TA-2005-0151+0+DOC+XML+V0//EN |archive-url = https://archive.is/20071226015809/http://www.europarl.eu.int/omk/sipade3?SAME_LEVEL=1&LEVEL=5&NAV=X&DETAIL=&PUBREF=-//EP//TEXT+TA+P6-TA-2005-0151+0+DOC+XML+V0//EN |url-status=dead |archi